<div class='row'>
  <div class='col s12'>
    <h3 class='center'>What isn't your tax software telling you?</h3>
    <br />
    <p class='flow-text'><strong>
      For little more than the price of over-the-counter software, that may not
      be asking all the right questions, you can email or deliver your tax
      documents to a professional tax preparer and be sure you're getting all
      the right answers.
    </strong></p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class='row'>
  <div class='col s12 m6 l4'>
    {{#md-card title='Step 1'
      image='assets/images/tt-step1.jpg'}}
      {{#md-card-content}}
        You will be provided with a tax organizer. Simply complete the
        questionnaire and place it, with required tax documents, in the
        pre-addressed envelope provided.
      {{/md-card-content}}
    {{/md-card}}
  </div>

  <div class='col s12 m6 l4'>
    {{#md-card title='Step 2'
      image='assets/images/tt-step2.jpg'}}
      {{#md-card-content}}
        Send your tax documents via email, post office, or drop off. There
        are also options to use photo, scan, or courier. It has never been
        easier to get your tax docuemnts to your preparer.
      {{/md-card-content}}
    {{/md-card}}
  </div>

  <div class='col s12 m6 l4'>
    {{#md-card title='Step 3'
      image='assets/images/tt-step3.png'}}
      {{#md-card-content}}
        You will be provided with a tax organizer. Simply complete the
        questionnaire and place it, with required tax documents, in the
        pre-addressed envelope provided.
      {{/md-card-content}}
    {{/md-card}}
  </div>
</div>

<div class='center-align'>
  {{#link-to 'register'}}
    {{md-btn text='MEET A PREPARER'
      buttonType='large'
      class='sign-up'
    }}
  {{/link-to}}
</div>
